These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, british, australian, canadian, indian, russian
1. the pakistani is in the middle##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the british##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the australian##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the british##1
5. the russian is on the far left##1
6. the indian is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | russian | australian | canadian | pakistani | british | turkish | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, security-guard, bartender, musician, mechanic, lawyer, writer
1. the writer is on the far right##1
2. the coach is on the far left##1
3. the coach is on the left of the mechanic##1
4. the mechanic is on the left of the bartender##1
5. the musician is on the right of the lawyer##1
6. the writer is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | coach | mechanic | bartender | lawyer | musician | security-guard | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, cooking, magic-tricks, singing, filmmaking, reading, baking
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | gardening | reading | magic-tricks | baking | cooking | singing |

 #################################

 
