1. the owner of the cat is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | rat | frog | hamster | cat | dog | horse | pony |

