3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | animation | epic | adventure | zombie | scientific | western |

